# Tidyverse

[Tidyverse](https://www.tidyverse.org/) is a set of R packages that are commonly used to transform data for analysis. These packages share the same philosophy and structure when fixing data.




::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
install.packages("tidyverse")
```
:::
